snippet.title: Cakefoot 🍰😈 Trailer | Ultra hard action game now in early-access and coming to Steam May 10th
snippet.description: Cakefoot is an ultra hard, single-button, minimalist avoid 'em up with natural physics. The cake moves on a rail -- hold to go forward, let go to fall back, avoiding enemy patterns. With an epic 22-level quest, arcade mode, unlockables, and local high scores, Cakefoot is endlessly replayable, and impossible to defeat. Play online now at https://cakefoot.dank.game and wishlist on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2869020/Cakefoot/
